Titolo: The Patrician (video game)

Anno: 1992

Descrizione: The Patrician (German: Der Patrizier) is a historical trading simulation video game for Amiga, Atari ST and MS-DOS developed by Ascaron Entertainment and published by Triptychon Software. In the game, the player assumes the role of a merchant in any of several cities of the Hanseatic League, accumulating money, capital and consumer goods, and real estate, expanding his company, and furthering his career at home and abroad.



Genere: Business simulation 

Valutazione: N/A
